fields.title: The complete Javascript course 2021: From zero to hero
fields.overview:
JavaScript is the most popular programming language in the world. It powers the entire modern web. It provides millions of high-paying jobs all over the world. This is the most complete JavaScript course on Udemy. It's an all-in-one package that will take you from the very fundamentals of JavaScript, all the way to building modern and complex applications.

You will learn modern JavaScript from the very beginning, step-by-step. I will guide you through practical and fun code examples, an important theory about how JavaScript works behind the scenes, and beautiful and complete projects.

You will also learn how to think like a developer, how to plan application features, how to architect your code, how to debug code, and a lot of other real-world skills that you will need on your developer job.
